io.github.iwyfewwnt.steamid.utils

Class USteamBit

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.iwyfewwnt.steamid.utils.USteamBit

  • public final class USteamBit
extends Object
    A Steam ID bits utility.

    USteamBit is the utility class for all Steam account type-64 identifier offsets and masks for its bit vector.
